        <title>Termux-安卓机ollama&#43;deepseek-R1部署</title>
        <link>https://ynhugo.github.io/p/termux-%E5%AE%89%E5%8D%93%E6%9C%BAollama-deepseek-r1%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/</link>
